00:44:07,560 --> 00:44:11,079
I am the man who will punish you, Agah Effendi.

512
00:44:11,399 --> 00:44:14,159
What's the punishment? I didn't kill anyone, it was all a dream.

513
00:44:14,399 --> 00:44:16,000
The prosecutor said so anyway!

514
00:44:16,479 --> 00:44:20,600
Your punishment starts from now on. You will suffer, there is no solution!

515
00:44:20,680 --> 00:44:22,880
What punishment, what did I do?

516
00:44:23,359 --> 00:44:26,800
That daughter, son-in-law, grandchild, all of you...

517
00:44:27,279 --> 00:44:29,479
I will bury it in the ground in such a way...

518
00:44:29,920 --> 00:44:32,159
Even if the whole world comes, they won't be able to find it.

519
00:44:32,359 --> 00:44:34,239
From where? I didn't do anything!

520
00:44:35,079 --> 00:44:36,760
You killed my brother.

521
00:44:36,960 --> 00:44:39,199
What's the point, why should I kill your brother?

522
00:44:39,319 --> 00:44:41,079
I don't know. You will remember.

523
00:44:41,359 --> 00:44:42,359
What will I remember?

524
00:44:43,439 --> 00:44:46,600
Your treatment is going a little slow, let me speed it up.

525
00:44:49,600 --> 00:44:51,880
- You'll remember this, right! - What is this?

526
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:57,159
This is the biggest crime you've ever committed!

527
00:45:00,359 --> 00:45:01,520
Personal…

528
00:45:04,560 --> 00:45:08,560
You made this my brother's destiny, Agah Effendi.

529
00:45:10,600 --> 00:45:14,000
But now, do you know what is written on your forehead?

530
00:45:15,720 --> 00:45:16,560
Kader.

531
00:45:17,439 --> 00:45:18,000
Is it?

532
00:45:18,319 --> 00:45:18,880
Sorry uncle!

533
00:45:23,880 --> 00:45:24,520
Dur!

534
00:45:25,640 --> 00:45:26,279
What will I remember!

535
00:45:33,119 --> 00:45:34,199
What does it matter?

536
00:45:35,560 --> 00:45:36,119
It's a relationship!

537
00:45:38,479 --> 00:45:39,000
It's a relationship!

538
00:45:42,800 --> 00:45:44,319
What will I remember!

